Definition: an Old Testament book telling how a Jewish official at the court of Artaxerxes I in 444 BC became a leader in rebuilding Jerusalem after the Babylonian Captivity
Synonyms: Book_of_Nehemiah, book, i, Writings, p, Old_Testament, an, Old, Testament, telling, how, a, Jewish, official, at, the, court, of, Artaxerxes, I, in, BC, became, leader, rebuilding, Jerusalem, after, Babylonian, Captivity
Category: noun.communication
